message.body: Hi. Do you still want to meet tonight?
I would like to hang out but I messed up my shoulders, I don't know about yoga
What happened? Oh no!

A nightmare at whole foods, we parked three blocks away because of parade traffic on Sunday and then I carried five bags to the car. I feel like I ripped both shoulders off. I'm seeing Jess on Thursday, it's so painful
Even smella had a bag
Wow. That is not what I was expecting.
What time works for you? 7:30 in old city? Or somewhere else?
I know, it's really lame
I can do old city. Is Pete coming? Should I invite Nate?
No. Pete is not coming. Invite Nate if you like!
Or we would get noodles in Chinatown...
Could
That sounds delicious, lets do that
Cool. Is there a place you prefer? There's nan Zhou... Or Rangoon
I don't really know any good places in Chinatown, I rarely go there anymore
Nan Zhou has good noodle soup. Rangoon has most variety but is a little more $$$.
More variety
I think Rangoon has alcohol. But man Zhou has the cocktail place, hop sing across the street. If that is a thing you want to do
Lets go to the one with the cocktail place : )
Cool. Nan Zhou it is. It's at 10th and race. Sometimes it's busy but I have a fall back...
I will have galoshes on
